Package com.example.rrmp.ramp_init

Class Professor

java.lang.Object
com.example.rrmp.ramp_init.Professor
public class Professor extends Object
Represents a professor entity with their associated details and ratings. This class is designed to work with JSON deserialization using Jackson annotations.
